Mountains , songs , friends , snow and what else you need . While trekking with them I learnt how to laugh from inside,  with them I didn't felt the cold temperature of -6°c because they kept me warm with their love and acceptance.  I was nothing but a stranger who wanted to trek and to make  youtube content . After few hours , I forgot all the struggle , cold , moto and went on developing a strong bond with those unknown personalities , i learnt them , I learnt their every movement , I learnt how to stay happy even if you are hopeless and fatigue. We shared each other's food , laughed on each other's jokes . They gave me their hands when I couldn't climb ... it is true that vibes matter the most but the most important thing is that we didn't knew each others name neither we remember them but all we carry is our " YAADON KA SUITCASE ".Life teaches you from every single perspective,  it teaches you to be open , it teaches you to set your soul free and sing out loud "Phir le aaya dil majboor kya keeje
Raas na aaya rehna door kya keeje
Dil keh raha use maqammal kar bhi aao
Wo jo adhoori si baat baaki hai
Wo jo adhoori si yaad baaki hai...."

If you haven't watched the vlog yet , go and watch it on youtube asap.😁❤️
.
